RUNAS(1)               General Commands Manual              RUNAS(1)

NAME
       runas - run command as another user

SYNOPSIS
       runas user cmd [ arg...  ]

DESCRIPTION
       Runas writes user to /dev/user and invokes cmd with the given
       arguments.  The command is only invoked  if  setting  of  the
       user name succeeds.

SOURCE
       /appl/cmd/runas.b

SEE ALSO
       cons(3),

                                                            RUNAS(1)
